{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think anybody went to the synagogue anymore after that, because very soon afterwards, the-- there was a law that by-- by a certain time, we had-- the Jews had to leave the provinces.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You no longer were allowed to live outside of the big cities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The provinces were anything outside Amsterdam or The Hague.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, Holland is 11 provinces, you know, that's-- that's-- and we we not allowed to live there anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now this was the end of '42 beginning of '43 when this came, OK?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- so my uncle, who had a big problem because he had to take care-- asides from his own family, he had to take care of two of us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he had this mother-in-law from his first wife living with him, OK?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's my-- my older cousin's grandmother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her name was Maita Woresack, and she was living there also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then there were three aunts also who were related to his-- not-- they were-- were not my aunts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't even remember their name, but they were living nearby.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were related to-- to-- to him through his first wife, and he was taking care of them too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Basically, he was paying for-- then for them to live with neighbors, but their food-- my aunt had to cook it for them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember I used to take-- that-- that's what I knew about that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to take them their food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In-- in-- in the afternoon, at night, I used to bring their food to them, hot food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the only thing I remember about them before-- when this situation arose, they-- they gave you time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't from today till tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By a certain date, we had to-- the provinces had to be what they called judenrein, clean of Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm sure you've heard the word before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, those three aunts-- it was winter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had the-- they had some sort of fire burning, and they got some of-- some sort of carbon monoxide poisoning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were taken to hospital, all three of them, OK?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't die at the time, but they all were taken to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to them afterwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know they didn't survive, but whether they were taken from the hospital to-- to a concentration camp, whether they died there, I don't know, OK?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we, in 1943, went-- were taken to a camp called Vught, which was a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when they said you had to move--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told us where to move to, OK?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there was two possibilities-- or to go into hiding, which some people did-- or to go where they told you to go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, the Germans, the difference between Dinxperlo and Amsterdam was in Amsterdam or The Hague or other big cities, they physically came to your door and dragged you out or took you out.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes if they were very civil, they let you-- they give you an hour to pack your things and then took you out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In-- in little villages like that, they didn't bother, you know, because it was too much.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they told you by certain hour, you have to be there, and then you go from there to there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So people complied and some of the people didn't comply.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they didn't stay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they went into hiding, some people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My uncle could have gone into hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had the opportunity through my-- through his brothers, through my-- through Adolf, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I know that-- I know that for a fact that he had been in touch and had offered him a possibility, but I think he was afraid.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His nerves-- I think his nerves were shot already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was taking care of everybody, and I'm sure he must have had huge money problems, which I, of course, as a little child, didn't realize to take care of everybody but he did.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and then of course, that-- that-- the nightly air raids didn't add to-- to-- to the-- to his comfort.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything was on his shoulders, so I don't think he had the nerves to-- to-- to go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you need those very strong nerves for that, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, when you went into hiding, you went to live in somebody's house usually.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't go into a forest like you did in-- in some other areas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Holland had no big forests anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You went to live in somebody's attic or somebody's cellar, and you couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were dependent on them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
